OTULEAR - The daRk side of OTULEA

Downloading
===========
cd /tmp
git clone git://github.com/nattomi/otulear.git

Installing the R package
========================
cd otulear
## before installing the package, edit the config file!
emacs -nw otulea/data/config.R
## f.i. 
## usersDir <- "/var/www/otulea/data/user/"
## alphalist <- "/var/www/otulea/data/item/alphalaist/alphalist.XML"
R CMD INSTALL otulea -l /usr/local/lib/R/site-library

Installing the develompment version of the web application
==========================================================
We assume that our Apache root folder is /var/www
cp -r otulea/inst/otulea.conf /etc/apache2/conf.d/
(then restart Apache)
mkdir /var/www/otulea
cp -r otulea/inst/www/data /var/www/otulea/data
mkdir /var/www/brew
cp -r otulea/inst/www/otulea.html /var/www/brew/
 

